00:23:59.720 --> 00:24:02.810
So it's spatially coherent,
but it's broadband,

00:24:02.810 --> 00:24:06.050
so you have temporally
incoherence.

00:24:06.050 --> 00:24:08.600
And the other kind
of this combination

00:24:08.600 --> 00:24:13.190
is temporally coherent, but
it's spatially incoherent.

00:24:13.190 --> 00:24:19.170
And it's typically referred
to as quasi-monochromatic--

00:24:19.170 --> 00:24:23.390
temporally coherent and
spatially incoherent.

00:24:23.390 --> 00:24:25.400
So if you put a
rotating diffuser, which

00:24:25.400 --> 00:24:31.400
is when you rotate the ground
glass or milky glass in front

00:24:31.400 --> 00:24:36.500
of the laser, then basically,
