00:29:55.040 --> 00:29:57.650
whose focal lengths
are f1 and f2.

00:29:57.650 --> 00:30:00.890
And typically, we put
our input transparency

00:30:00.890 --> 00:30:03.290
grating at the input plane.

00:30:03.290 --> 00:30:07.610
And we illuminate with the
