transform of the ATF.

00:31:09.320 --> 00:31:12.800
Or you can say it's field
transform [INAUDIBLE] function.

00:31:12.800 --> 00:31:16.000
So this is the coherent
point spread function.

00:31:16.000 --> 00:31:19.840
And you can define [INAUDIBLE]
function reduce coordinate.

00:31:19.840 --> 00:31:23.530
And the relation between
input and output field

00:31:23.530 --> 00:31:25.180
is this convolution.

00:31:25.180 --> 00:31:28.180
So G output-- I
mean, output field

00:31:28.180 --> 00:31:31.000
is convolution of
input field, and this

00:31:31.000 --> 00:31:33.070
is coherent point
spread function

00:31:33.070 --> 00:31:36.010
which is defined in field.

00:31:36.010 --> 00:31:41.210
So this is the stuff
that we all know.

00:31:41.210 --> 00:31:47.140
So the next thing is let me put
