and a to--

00:32:37.570 --> 00:32:38.710
e to the phi 2.

00:32:38.710 --> 00:32:42.230
But the bottom line
is in coherent case,

00:32:42.230 --> 00:32:46.250
I just have coherent
addition of two point spread

00:32:46.250 --> 00:32:48.640
functions like this.

00:32:48.640 --> 00:32:51.620
